This paper involves the development of a data-driven framework for robust taxi dispatch, which involves the use of machine learning and optimization techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), systems and control (cs.SY), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and robotics (cs.RO).
